calculationItems.name: YoY
calculationItems.expression:
// Tom Sampson © Clutch.Net 2023 MIT License
// 2023-09-17 00:15:34
VAR PY =
    CALCULATE(
        SELECTEDMEASURE( ),
        FILTER(
            ALL( Calendar ),
            Calendar[FiscalDate] >= MIN( Calendar[FiscalPYDate] )
                && Calendar[FiscalDate] <= MAX( Calendar[FiscalPYDate] )
        )
    )
VAR CY = SELECTEDMEASURE( )
VAR Result = IF( NOT ISBLANK( CY ) && NOT ISBLANK( PY ), CY - PY )
RETURN
    Result
